      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How many episodes of Law and Order SVU are there?</summary>
        <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">As of the conclusion of Season 25, there are 551 episodes of Law & Order: Special Victims Unit. Season 26 is currently airing, which will increase the total episode count well past 570 by its finale in 2025.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What is the longest running season of Law & Order SVU?</summary>
        <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">Seasons 4 and 5 are the longest-running seasons of Law & Order: SVU, each containing exactly 25 episodes. This massive output during the early 2000s cemented the show's dominance on network television.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Who has been in every season of Law and Order SVU?</summary>
